50:22.240 --> 50:27.560
Once you realize the architecture is hiding in plain sight, you begin to see it in every aspect of human behavior.

50:27.560 --> 50:31.420
You will certainly never look at a small red wooden box the same way again.

50:31.780 --> 50:35.200
Thank you for venturing into the persistence hierarchy with us on this deep dive.

50:35.620 --> 50:39.640
